text: Pataura is a village development committee in Rautahat District in the Narayani Zone of south-eastern Nepal. At the time of the 1991 Nepal census it had a population of 4521 people living in 794 individual households. ==See also== * Pataura, a village in Jaunpur, India Ajay Verma lives here. He is very known popular here. ==References== Category:Populated places in Rautahat District
title: Pataura, Nepal
